  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/0374b706c547465b6870b79cd598722f.webp?t=1759983887\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, Hiro, visits his relative's house in the countryside by himself.<br>This is a pixel art simulation game where you live under one roof for a month with three sisters, your childhood friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How you spend your time is up to you!<br>You can fish in the ocean or a river, have your catch cooked, build a secret base...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village is full of interesting folks, like the fisherman, the candy store owner, and your neighbors. <br>Complete their requests and they might reward you...!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make this month full of memories of your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/8657dcdb1c77568fb9acff006e04ad96.webp?t=1759983887\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/84e42a564e83f91ed3472b5230d61b11.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haruka</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The older sister who is always nice to you and great at cooking.<br>Her food is so good, you could never get tired of it. In fact, you always end up overeating...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/c63bfae60893ab6af3c52f9c1dff772d.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yui</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The closest person in age to you.<br>She's got a ton of toys and knows how to use them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/705ae7872f7b511cd19596ef77c2e79a.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Natsumi</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An older girl who has a cool, calm air about her.<br>She usually helps out at the shrine, and her hobby is playing guitar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/29960539a82e1d5b887b00ea8dbdace0.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rena</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A strange girl you meet at your secret base.<br>It seems like she's not from around here, but that's not the only weird thing about her...</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/0374b706c547465b6870b79cd598722f.webp?t=1759983887\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, Hiro, visits his relative's house in the countryside by himself.<br>This is a pixel art simulation game where you live under one roof for a month with three sisters, your childhood friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How you spend your time is up to you!<br>You can fish in the ocean or a river, have your catch cooked, build a secret base...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village is full of interesting folks, like the fisherman, the candy store owner, and your neighbors. <br>Complete their requests and they might reward you...!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make this month full of memories of your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/8657dcdb1c77568fb9acff006e04ad96.webp?t=1759983887\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/84e42a564e83f91ed3472b5230d61b11.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haruka</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The older sister who is always nice to you and great at cooking.<br>Her food is so good, you could never get tired of it. In fact, you always end up overeating...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/c63bfae60893ab6af3c52f9c1dff772d.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yui</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The closest person in age to you.<br>She's got a ton of toys and knows how to use them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/705ae7872f7b511cd19596ef77c2e79a.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Natsumi</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An older girl who has a cool, calm air about her.<br>She usually helps out at the shrine, and her hobby is playing guitar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/29960539a82e1d5b887b00ea8dbdace0.avif?t=1759983887\" width=144 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rena</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A strange girl you meet at your secret base.<br>It seems like she's not from around here, but that's not the only weird thing about her...</p>",
